      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to prohibit recipients of disaster recovery relief assistance from the Department of Housing and Urban Development from penalizing applicants that declined assistance from the Small Business Administration.</title>
      </item>
